cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.GT. 

This paper involves reinforcement learning and neural networks, which are common topics in the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of neural networks for predicting certainty also falls under the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The implementation of the Pong game involves computer vision, which is a topic in the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the use of game theory in optimizing the agent's performance could also fall under the sub-category of cs.GT (Game Theory).
